{
  "texts": [
    "In testing, an RL agent interacts with the application (UI or API), learning optimal paths to uncover bugs, reach hidden functionality, or trigger rare conditions.",
    "Process Flow:  Agent starts with no knowledge of the app.",
    " It explores possible actions (e.g., button clicks, form entries).",
    " Rewards are given when new states, crashes, or unexpected behaviors are discovered.",
    " The agent improves its strategy over time."
  ]
}